      h: 560

        label: "RuBP"

        color: "orange"
      - id: glucose

        color: "red"

        dst: rubisco
        label: "CO₂ binding"
      - src: rubp
        dst: rubisco
        label: "Substrate"
      - src: rubisco
        dst: glucose
        label: "Glucose synthesis"
